article.linkText: Penn scores 21 to carry Drake over Indiana State 73-66
article.story: TERRE HAUTE, Ind. -- — Roman Penn had 21 points as Drake won its 11th straight game, getting past Indiana State 73-66 on Monday. Joseph Yesufu had 13 points for Drake (11-0, 2-0 Missouri Valley Conference). Shanquan Hemphill added 12 points and Darnell Brodie had 10 points and eight rebounds. Jake LaRavia had 20 points for the Sycamores (3-4, 0-2). Cooper Neese added 18 points.
